Topological Taxonomy of a Theory of Everything (ToE)
|
├── I. Geometric-Topological Foundations
|   ├── A. Manifold-Based
|   |   ├── 1. Riemannian Manifolds (GR-like)
|   |   └── 2. Non-Commutative Manifolds
|   └── B. Discrete Topologies
|       ├── 1. Causal Sets
|       └── 2. Spin Networks / Spin Foams
|
├── II. Symmetry Group Frameworks
|   ├── A. Lie Group-Based
|   |   ├── 1. SU(5), SO(10) GUTs
|   |   └── 2. E₈ Unification Theories
|   └── B. Supersymmetry (SUSY)
|       ├── 1. Supergravity
|       └── 2. Superstring Theories
|
├── III. Dimensional Extensions
|   ├── A. Extra Dimensions
|   |   ├── 1. Kaluza-Klein Models
|   |   └── 2. Braneworld Scenarios
|   └── B. Holographic Models
|       └── 1. AdS/CFT Correspondence
|
├── IV. Quantum Topology Approaches
|   ├── A. Loop Quantum Gravity
|   ├── B. Topological Quantum Field Theory (TQFT)
|   └── C. Knot/Link Invariants (Jones Polynomial, etc.)
|
└── V. Information-Theoretic Topodynamics
    ├── A. Holographic Entropy & Area Laws
    ├── B. Quantum Error Correction Models
    └── C. Computational/Topological Causality Theories
